@startuml name
title LBH FSS Public API — System Scope

actor "Client" as client

rectangle "AWS (eu-west-2)" {
  rectangle "VPC" as vpc {
    rectangle "Private Subnets" as subnets {
      node "Lambda\nfss-public-api" as lambda
      database "RDS PostgreSQL" as rds
    }
    rectangle "Public Subnet" as publicsubnet
  }

  node "API Gateway" as apigw
}

client --> apigw : HTTPS
apigw --> lambda : Invoke
lambda --> rds : SQL (VPC)

note right of lambda
Uses SSM Parameter Store for:
- DB creds
- External API config
end note

@enduml